CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 13, 1945, pg. 14 reads: "Happy Birthday To You - Miss Bettie Lou Tarplay of Deary Street was honored at a surprise party on her tenth birthday, Sept. 26. Guests included Barbara Jean, Louise and Betty Lou Roberts, Terry and Bobby Edwards, Carol, Lorraine nad Butch Tarplay, Tommy and Russell Greene, Juanita Allen, Gerald Strothers, Norma, Billy and Wilson Oden, Edith and Sonny Swan. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of birthday party, including Barbara Jean Roberts, Louise Roberts, Betty Lou Roberts, Terry Edwards, Bobby Edwards, Carol Tarplay, Lorraine Tarplay, Butch Tarplay, Tommy Greene, Russell Greene, Juanita Allen, Gerald Strothers, Norma Oden, Billy Oden, Wilson Oden, Edith Swan, Sonny Swan, and unknown woman, possibly Mrs. Tarplay, posed around Bettie Lou Tarplay standing behind her birthday cake, in Tarplay home on Deary Street
